
TENTATIVE PROJECT GOAL:
-Scrape cocktail recipes from external sources for cross-referencing with DD products.
-Retain and organize recipe data for customer querying/filtering based on products.
-Recommend DD products based on cocktail recipe preferences.

TENTATIVE PROJECT STRUCTURE:
-Python scraper to retrieve cocktail names, recipe, and ingredients.
-Data cleaning layer to generalize liquors/ingredients as needed.
-Database (or maybe just generic data structure) to retain cocktail data.
-Database (or maybe just generic data structure) to retain DD product data.
-Some way to link associated products to their recipe counterparts.
-Dashboard for Jason (?)
-Web component for online customers.


